    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-cared for, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior maintains a strong finish and a nice shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular driving. Inside, the interior is clean and well-preserved, with only mild wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it remains very sound with a documented service history, ensuring it is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 35500.0,
