    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go and runs like a champ. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a test drive and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. It's equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, providing mechanical engagement that modern dual-clutch systems cannot replicate. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent inspection of the rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. The M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal power delivery through the corners. While showing signs of honest use consistent with a well-maintained driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a healthy double VANOS system. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
